channels.name: your-projects
channels.topic:
Do you have a great, big and good idea? Post it here!
Post here DIY things related, or code etc... that you wanna share with us.
**Don't forget that advertising (for discord servers, ask it to a mod) is still prohibited, so post a project that you are developping/creating in a, experimental purpose**

__To post images & integrate links, you need to have the role GA Member__

**You must follow this post format:**
__Name:__
__Type:__
__Author(s):__
__Description:__
__Links__:
__Pictures (optional):__

Example: a github project, some pictures of your new homemade RC car, etc...

channels.name: post-your-naked-steam-keys
channels.topic:
Feeling grateful? Post your key here!
If you see a key that doesn't have the :key: Reaction beneath it, then it is not used!
If you used a key, give the :key: reaction to it! Thanks!
Do not talk here (use reactions)
:warning:️**KEYS CAN BE DUPE**, that's normal,  don't to post it that's dupe, since everyone has the access to this channel. Report any spams.

channels.topic:
**See the rules in <#300634008323358730> before.**
Free games! Free! Free!

WARNING: IF THE WEBSITE ASKS PERSONAL INFORMATION SUCH AS CELLPHONE NUMBERS, ID, HUMAN VERIFICATION, CLICK THE WEBSITE AWAY IMMEDIATELY!

channels.name: moderator-room
channels.topic:
The Room where our 'Magic' happens!
The Moderation Commands
-?warn [user] [reason]: Warn an user with dynobot. Before using that command, warn the user verbally
-?mute [user] [time] [reason]
-?unmute [user]
-?modlogs [user]: Display warning and mute cases for an user
-?ban [@usermention] [reason]: Ban an user. You can execute that command every hour
or
-?ban [id] [reason]
